item.description: About me Hey there, My name is Cam. Here’s a stream of consciousness and a little about what lead me to IT. I spent a lot of time doing very hard manual labour in some pretty average places, the best being a stint in a heat treatment plant. I was tasked, with my friend Tomas, to restore an old steel quenching furnace. This is the process of cooking steel at 900 degrees, and then dropping it into hot oil.
